Rating: 4
My guests raved about this. They all thought it had a peppermint candy taste and couldn't guess the cardamon.

Rating: 4
oh, and to add: a previous reviewer said to strain the cardamom out after a few hours because the flavor was too strong... i totally disagree. i left the pods in for a full 24 hours and i thought the flavor was delightful. but, as they say, in matters of taste, there is no argument... i might agree with other reviewers that it is quite sweet, and might cut the sugar in the future, but it's certainly not cloying. the recipe is lovely as it stands.

Rating: 4
made this into an ice cream, as suggested, and good lord, was it delicious...

